This paper is about developing an end-to-end dialogue system for recommendation, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and human-computer interaction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers topics related to natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves training models using self-supervised bot-play, which falls under the category of reinforcement learning and can be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval and recommendation systems, which can be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
